  "prompt": "I told her I like her, now what?",
  "response": "Expressing your feelings is a brave step! Here are some suggestions on what to do next:\n\n1. **Gauge Her Reaction**: Pay attention to how she responds. Is she interested, surprised, or uncertain? Her body language and verbal cues can provide insight into her feelings.\n\n2. **Give Her Space**: If she needs time to process your confession, give her that space. Don\u2019t pressure her for an immediate response.\n\n3. **Communication**: Keep the lines of communication open. You can ask her how she feels or if she wants to talk more about it.\n\n4. **Be Honest**: If she shares her feelings, be honest about yours, whether she reciprocates or not. If she needs time, reassure her that you're willing to wait.\n\n5. **Respect Her Feelings**: Whatever her response is, it\u2019s important to respect her feelings. If she doesn\u2019t feel the same way, try not to take it personally.\n\n6. **Plan a Casual Follow-Up**: If things are looking positive, suggest hanging out more to build your relationship naturally.\n\n7. **Stay Positive**: Regardless of her response, remember that being open about your feelings is a big step, and it's great that you took that chance.\n\nUltimately, just be yourself and let things unfold naturally!",
